trans-unit.note: An error message displayed in a tooltip on VDT nodes when no dimension was select for the nodes to display on the columns. Only time dimensions are allowed.

trans-unit.source: The following filter dimensions are no longer present: '{0}'.
trans-unit.note: An error message displayed in a tooltip on VDT nodes when at least one filter dimension is no longer present. The argument is a list of dimension ids which do not exists.
